Method Detail

execute

public void execute()
Executes menu item. If the item was 'remove anchor', tell server to remove the node with that anchor from the graph; if the item was 'remove property', check (if there is more than 1 value) which values the user wishes to remove, and tell the server.

isShowing

public boolean isShowing()
Check whether the pop-up is displayed

onClick

public void onClick(Widget sender)
Should be called when user clicks 'remove all values' or 'remove selected values' (or cancel, obviously). Tells server what to remove.

Parameters:
sender - Button Widget
